<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="3289866">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3289866/" class="title-link">值得一读</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3289866"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/4420423/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u4420423-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/4420423/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">bomburstic</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-05-23"
      class="main-meta">2010-05-23 14:22:00</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3289866_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  将传统意义上道德说教的儒家精神放在一个更具现实意义和人文关怀的维度上进行阐释，剥离人们对传统文化腐朽没落中庸无用的偏见，使得在中国流淌了几千年的传统文化核心重现鲜活生机的面孔。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">3有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_3289866_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_3289866_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="6288807">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6288807/" class="title-link">有独特之处</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6288807"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/77656985/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u77656985-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/77656985/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">ruzhe</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-09-20"
      class="main-meta">2013-09-20 16:05:36</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6288807_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  在目前的大陆儒者中，张祥龙先生是有独特之处的，此书值得一读。若在广州的话，此书可以去希圣书馆借阅，希圣书馆是文史哲共享型书馆。书馆及借阅详情见：http://www.douban.com/note/301941935/

